    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really does feel like that. just constant weight. and like you said, it's so quiet. it makes me wonder if there's actually any difference between being here and just... not being here. i feel like if i just stopped trying, if i just let go, everything would just be peaceful. like it would finally be over.",
